Installation instructions for Semantic Rules extension v1.01
---------------------------------------------------------------

Requirements: 
=============

    MediaWiki 1.15 or higher
    SMW 1.5
    SMWHalo 1.5 

Installation:
=============
   
Run:
php {wiki-path}/extensions/SemanticRules/maintenance/setup.php

Then add to your LocalSettings.php after you initialized SMWHalo:

require_once("extensions/SemanticRules/includes/SR_Initialize.php");


